<p><a name="Filmography" id="Filmography"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Christopher_Hitchens&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Filmography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Filmography</span></h2>
