<p><a name="Bibliography" id="Bibliography"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Christopher_Hitchens&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bibliography</span></h2>
<p><a name="As_sole_author" id="As_sole_author"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Christopher_Hitchens&amp;action=edit&amp;section=36" title="Edit section: As sole author">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">As sole author</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>2007 <i><a href="/wiki/God_is_not_Great" title="God is not Great" class="mw-redirect">God Is Not Great: How Religion Poisons Everything</a></i>. Twelve/Hachette Book Group USA/Warner Books, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0446579807" class="internal">ISBN 0446579807</a> / Published in the UK as <i><a href="/wiki/God_is_not_Great" title="God is not Great" class="mw-redirect">God Is Not Great: The Case Against Religion</a></i>. Atlantic Books, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781843545866" class="internal">ISBN 978-1-84354-586-6</a></li>
<li>2006 <i><a href="/wiki/Thomas_Paine%27s_%22Rights_of_Man%22:_A_Biography" title="Thomas Paine's &quot;Rights of Man&quot;: A Biography" class="mw-redirect">Thomas Paine's "Rights of Man": A Biography</a></i>. Books That Shook the World/Atlantic Books, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1843545136" class="internal">ISBN 1-84354-513-6</a></li>
